// Configuration settings file for Time of Life — Debug.
// API base URL is injected via Info.plist so runtime code can read it.

// xcconfig treats `//` as a comment, so we break it with an empty variable.
// The $(EMPTY) reference expands to nothing, resulting in http://127.0.0.1:8080.
EMPTY =
API_BASE_URL = http:/$(EMPTY)/127.0.0.1:8080